query:
SELECT refs.id AS "child_id!"
            FROM refs
            JOIN snapshots ON snapshots.id = refs.head
            WHERE ((snapshots.content->'analysisOf'->>'_id')::uuid = $1
                   OR (snapshots.content->'diagramIn'->>'_id')::uuid = $1)
              AND get_max_permission($2, refs.id) >= 'read'
